<div class="padding-top-md">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-push-8">
            <h4>Before you start a discussion...</h4>
            <p>There may be other students who have already asked the same question. You should <span class="codaisseur-color">do a quick search first</span> to make sure your question is unique. </p>
            <p>The best way to get the answers you're looking for is to learn <span class="codaisseur-color">how to ask good questions.</span> Get tips on how to ask good questions to get answers more quickly.</p>
            <p>If you're experiencing what appears to be a bug or something that doesn't seem to be working correctly, please <span class="codaisseur-color">contact support directly.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-pull-4">
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <%= render 'form', question: @question %>
                <hr>
                <small>Reference this <a href="http://assemble.io/docs/Cheatsheet-Markdown.html"><b>Markdown Cheatsheet</b></a> for syntax examples for formatting your question.</small>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>
</div>